Global comedy superstar Kevin Hart is in South Africa. In this eNCA exclusive, eNCA senior reporter Silindelo Masikane sat down with him to talk about his career, his comedy tour and his latest movie ‘Die Hart’. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Global comedy superstar and actor Kevin Hart is in South Africa. Hart is in the country for a tour. His last visit to the country was in 2016 for his ‘What Now?’ Tour. eNCA's Silindelo Masikane has more details in the video above.